/*                                                                            */
/*                                                                            */
/*                          Digital Scratch Library                           */
/*                   A motion detector for vinyl turntable                    */
/*                                                                            */
/*                                                                            */
/*============================================================================*/


Digital Scratch library is designed to analyze motion on vinyl turntable. It
requires usage of a specific timecoded vinyl disc.

Input: signal coming from turntable playing a timecoded vinyl disc.
Output: motion parameters (speed, direction and volume).

A common usage would be to drive an audio player. As a result a DJ is able to
mix digital audio files using regular vinyl turntables.

DigitalScratch library is under GNU/GPL3 licence.


More informations on : http://www.digital-scratch.org

Author : Julien Rosener <julien.rosener@digital-scratch.org>
